---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="flex flex-col min-h-screen items-center justify-center px-6 py-20 bg-transparent relative">
    <div class="max-w-2xl w-full text-center z-10">
      <h1 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl font-black bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-pink-400 to-yellow-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-6 tracking-tight">
        Certificaciones
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-medium text-white/80 mb-6">
        | AWS Associate| AWS Professional | Github |&nbsp; 
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10">
        Diseño y gestiono infraestructuras cloud modernas, seguras y escalables para startups y empresas que quieren crecer rápido y sin límites.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
        <a href="#sobre-mi" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 hover:bg-cyan-400 text-white font-semibold shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 text-base group">
          <span>Conócelas</span>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down ml-2 group-hover:translate-y-1 transition-transform"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="./proyectos" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 text-cyan-300 font-semibold shadow-lg transition-all duration-200 text-base border border-cyan-400/30">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket mr-2"></i>
          Proyectos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <section class="mt-16 mb-40">
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-pink-400 to-yellow-300 mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3 justify-center">
        &gt; Obtenidos
      </h2>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl text-center mb-10 leading-relaxed mx-auto">
      Estas son las certificaciones que actualmente estoy preparando. Reflejan mi compromiso continuo con el aprendizaje y la mejora profesional en el ámbito de la tecnología y la nube.
    </p>
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Terminal AWS Solutions Architect -->
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-cyan-400/30 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-lg hover:scale-[1.025] transition-transform duration-200 min-w-[420px] md:min-w-[560px]">
        <div class="flex items-center px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-800/70 to-slate-800/70 border-b border-cyan-400/10">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          <span class="ml-4 text-green-400 font-mono text-sm">bash</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-10 py-6 font-mono text-green-200 text-base bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900/40 to-slate-900/40">
          <p>
            <span class="text-cyan-400">nacho@certificaciones</span>:<span class="text-yellow-400">~</span>$ <span class="text-white">cat aws_solutions_architect.txt</span>
          </p>
          <div class="h-3"></div>
          <p>
            <span class="text-cyan-300">Certificado:</span> AWS Certified Solutions Architect - Associate
            <br>
            <span class="text-cyan-300">Descripción:</span> Este certificado valida la capacidad para diseñar y desplegar sistemas escalables en AWS.
            <br>
            <span class="text-cyan-300">Enlace:</span>
            <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-solutions-architect-associate/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300 transition">Más información</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center pb-6">
          <img src="/public/practicioner.png" alt="AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Badge" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" loading="lazy">
          <span class="text-green-300 text-sm text-center">Logo oficial de AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Terminal Azure Administrator -->
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-blue-400/30 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-lg hover:scale-[1.025] transition-transform duration-200 min-w-[420px] md:min-w-[560px]">
        <div class="flex items-center px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800/70 to-slate-800/70 border-b border-blue-400/10">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          <span class="ml-4 text-blue-300 font-mono text-sm">bash</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-10 py-6 font-mono text-blue-200 text-base bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/40 to-slate-900/40">
          <p>
            <span class="text-blue-400">nacho@certificaciones</span>:<span class="text-yellow-400">~</span>$ <span class="text-white">cat azure_administrator.txt</span>
          </p>
          <div class="h-3"></div>
          <p>
            <span class="text-blue-300">Certificado:</span> Microsoft Certified: Azure Administrator Associate
            <br>
            <span class="text-blue-300">Descripción:</span> Este certificado demuestra la habilidad para implementar, gestionar y monitorear entornos de Azure.
            <br>
            <span class="text-blue-300">Enlace:</span>
            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/certifications/azure-administrator/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300 transition">Más información</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center pb-6">
          <img src="https://d1.awsstatic.com/training-and-certification/Certification%20Badges/AWS-Certified-Cloud-Practitioner_badge.8a0e0bfb1b2b8e2e6e7c1b2e6e7c1b2e.png" alt="AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Badge" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" loading="lazy">
          <span class="text-green-300 text-sm text-center">Logo oficial de AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 mb-40">
    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
      <h2 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-pink-400 to-yellow-300 mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg flex items-center gap-3 justify-center">
        &gt; En Proceso 
      </h2>    
    </div>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl text-center mb-10 leading-relaxed mx-auto">
      Estas son las certificaciones que actualmente estoy preparando. Reflejan mi compromiso continuo con el aprendizaje y la mejora profesional en el ámbito de la tecnología y la nube.
    </p>
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Terminal AWS Cloud Practitioner -->
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-green-400/30 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-lg hover:scale-[1.025] transition-transform duration-200 min-w-[420px] md:min-w-[560px]">
        <div class="flex items-center px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-800/70 to-slate-800/70 border-b border-green-400/10">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          <span class="ml-4 text-green-300 font-mono text-sm">bash</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-10 py-6 font-mono text-green-200 text-base bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/40 to-slate-900/40">
          <p>
            <span class="text-green-400">nacho@certificaciones</span>:<span class="text-yellow-400">~</span>$ <span class="text-white">cat aws_cloud_practitioner.txt</span>
          </p>
          <div class="h-3"></div>
          <p>
            <span class="text-green-300">Certificado:</span> AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner (CLF-01)
            <br>
            <span class="text-green-300">Descripción:</span> Este certificado se centra en las habilidades para gestionar servicios e infraestructura en la nube de AWS.
            <br>
            <span class="text-green-300">Enlace:</span>
            <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-cloud-practitioner/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300 transition">Más información</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center pb-6">
          <img src="https://d1.awsstatic.com/training-and-certification/Certification%20Badges/AWS-Certified-Cloud-Practitioner_badge.8a0e0bfb1b2b8e2e6e7c1b2e6e7c1b2e.png" alt="AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Badge" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" loading="lazy">
          <span class="text-green-300 text-sm text-center">Logo oficial de AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Terminal Linux Foundation Certified System Administrator -->
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-400/30 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-lg hover:scale-[1.025] transition-transform duration-200 min-w-[420px] md:min-w-[560px]">
        <div class="flex items-center px-6 py-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-800/70 to-slate-900/70 border-b border-slate-400/10">
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-red-500 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400 mr-2"></span>
          <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          <span class="ml-4 text-slate-300 font-mono text-sm">bash</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-10 py-6 font-mono text-slate-200 text-base bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900/40 to-slate-800/40">
          <p>
            <span class="text-slate-400">nacho@certificaciones</span>:<span class="text-yellow-400">~</span>$ <span class="text-white">cat linux_foundation_csa.txt</span>
          </p>
          <div class="h-3"></div>
          <p>
            <span class="text-slate-300">Certificado:</span> Linux Foundation Certified System Administrator (LFCS)
            <br>
            <span class="text-slate-300">Descripción:</span> Este certificado se centra en las habilidades para la administración de sistemas operativos basados en LINUX/UNIX.
            <br>
            <span class="text-slate-300">Enlace:</span>
            <a href="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certification/linux-foundation-certified-sysadmin-lfcs/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline hover:text-blue-300 transition">Más información</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col items-center pb-6">
          <img src="https://training.linuxfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/LFCS_Badge_Black.png" alt="Linux Foundation Certified System Administrator Badge" class="w-24 h-24 mb-2" loading="lazy">
          <span class="text-slate-300 text-sm text-center">Logo oficial de Linux Foundation Certified System Administrator</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>